00237 // test the algorithm params
00238 void FusionCHPDataGCOSTest::AlgParamsTest(string fileName)
00239 {
00240         CCHPFileData gcosChp;
00241         gcosChp.SetFileName(fileName.c_str());
00242         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_MESSAGE("Failed: Read header!", gcosChp.ReadHeader() == true);
00243         FusionCHPData *chp = FusionCHPDataReg::ReadHeader(fileName);
00244         FusionCHPLegacyData *fusionChp = FusionCHPLegacyData::FromBase(chp);
00245         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionChp != NULL);
00246 
00247     FusionTagValuePairTypeList algParamsFusion;
00248     fusionChp->GetHeader().AlgorithmParameters(algParamsFusion);
00249     FusionTagValuePairTypeList::iterator beginFusion = algParamsFusion.begin();
00250     FusionTagValuePairTypeList::iterator endFusion = algParamsFusion.end();
00251 
00252         TagValuePairTypeList& algParamsGCOS = gcosChp.GetHeader().AlgorithmParameters();
00253         TagValuePairTypeList::iterator beginGCOS = algParamsGCOS.begin(), endGCOS = algParamsGCOS.end();
00254 
00255         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_MESSAGE("Failed: Compare - alg count",fusionChp->GetHeader().AlgorithmParameterCount() == gcosChp.GetHeader().AlgorithmParameters().size());
00256 
00257         typedef map<wstring,wstring,less<wstring> > theFusionMap;
00258         theFusionMap map;
00259 
00260         // need the map to have an easy lookup for the key to see if the fusion has the key
00261         for (; beginFusion != endFusion; beginFusion++)
00262         {
00263                 map.insert(theFusionMap::value_type(beginFusion->Tag,beginFusion->Value));
00264         }
00265 
00266         theFusionMap::const_iterator findIt;
00267         for(; beginGCOS != endGCOS; beginGCOS++)
00268         {
00269                 // test single alg value call
00270                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT_MESSAGE("Failed: Compare Algorithm Parameter!", fusionChp->GetHeader().GetAlgorithmParameter(StringUtils::ConvertMBSToWCS(beginGCOS->Tag).c_str()) == StringUtils::ConvertMBSToWCS(beginGCOS->Value));
00271 
00272                 // test to see if the keys and values are the same between what was retrieved from fusion get algorithm params and
00273                 // with what was retrieved by the gcos api
00274                 findIt = map.find(StringUtils::ConvertMBSToWCS(beginGCOS->Tag));
00275                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT_MESSAGE("Faile: Algorithm parameter not found in Fusion list", findIt != map.end());
00276                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT_MESSAGE("Faile: Algorithm parameter not found in Fusion list", findIt->second == StringUtils::ConvertMBSToWCS(beginGCOS->Value));
00277         }
00278         delete fusionChp;
00279 }

00339 // tests the algorithm parameters
00340 void FusionCHPDataGCOSTest::ReadHeaderAndVerifyAlgParamsTest(string fileName)
00341 {
00342         // read the header with the fusion api
00343         FusionCHPData *chp = FusionCHPDataReg::ReadHeader(fileName);
00344         FusionCHPLegacyData *fusionChp = FusionCHPLegacyData::FromBase(chp);
00345         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionChp != NULL);
00346 
00347         // read the header with the gcos api
00348         CCHPFileData gcosChp;
00349         gcosChp.SetFileName(fileName.c_str());
00350         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_MESSAGE("Failed: Read header!", gcosChp.ReadHeader() == true);
00351 
00352         // get the gcos list
00353         TagValuePairTypeList listGCOS = gcosChp.GetHeader().AlgorithmParameters();
00354         FusionTagValuePairTypeList listFusion;
00355         // get the fusion list
00356         fusionChp->GetHeader().AlgorithmParameters(listFusion);
00357 
00358         // test that the number of parameters are the same between a pure gcos file sdk call and the fusdion api call
00359         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_MESSAGE("Failed: Compare - alg param count",listFusion.size() == listGCOS.size());
00360 
00361         // this section will test that the parameters read by both the pure gcos api and the fusion are the same
00362         // first we get the interators for the loop
00363         FusionTagValuePairTypeList::iterator begin = listFusion.begin();
00364         FusionTagValuePairTypeList::iterator end = listFusion.end();
00365 
00366         // loop over every parameter in the fusion parameter list and use it to get the value thru the getalgorithmparameter call
00367         // we could of used the value property of the of the iterator that is from the fusion algorithm list retrieved
00368         // early, but this is to exerise the get individual alg params api for both.
00369         // However, I will test the interator Value property from the fusion list and compare it to the other values returned from the
00370         // the get alg parameter calls
00371         for (; begin != end; begin++)
00372         {
00373                 // get the fusion value for the parameter name
00374                 wstring tempFusion = fusionChp->GetHeader().GetAlgorithmParameter(begin->Tag.c_str());
00375                 // get the gcos value for the parameter name
00376                 // have to convert the string to wstring first though
00377                 wstring tempGCOS = StringUtils::ConvertMBSToWCS(gcosChp.GetHeader().GetAlgorithmParameter(StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(begin->Tag).c_str()));
00378 
00379                 // double check that the value from the fusion list is the same as the other values retieved from the get alg params calls
00380                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT_MESSAGE("Failed: Compare - params",tempFusion == tempGCOS && begin->Value == tempGCOS);
00381         }
00382         delete fusionChp;
00383 }

00642 // tests the background data for the chp file. This tests the backgroundzones, backgroundinfo and backgroundtype for each zone
00643 void FusionCHPDataGCOSTest::BackgroundDataTest(string fileName)
00644 {
00645         CPPUNIT_ADDITIONALMESSAGE_H
00646         // here we compare the background data contents with both the gcos reader and the fusion reader and they better be the same
00647         FusionCHPData *chp = FusionCHPDataReg::ReadHeader(fileName);

00649         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionChp != NULL);

00653         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_MESSAGE("Failed: Read header!", gcosChp.ReadHeader() == true);
00654 
00655         BackgroundZoneInfo zoneInfoFusion;

00657         BackgroundZoneInfo zoneInfoGCOS = gcosChp.GetHeader().GetBackgroundZoneInfo();
00658 
00659         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_MESSAGE("Failed: Compare - number_zones",zoneInfoFusion.number_zones == zoneInfoGCOS.number_zones);
00660         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_MESSAGE("Failed: Compare - smooth_factor",zoneInfoFusion.smooth_factor == zoneInfoGCOS.smooth_factor);
00661         BackgroundZoneTypeList zonesFusion = zoneInfoFusion.zones;
00662         BackgroundZoneTypeList zonesGCOS = zoneInfoGCOS.zones;
00663 
00664         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_MESSAGE("Failed: Compare - GetChangeString",zonesFusion.size() == zonesGCOS.size());
00665 
00666         BackgroundZoneTypeList::iterator beginFusion = zonesFusion.begin(), endFusion = zonesFusion.end();
00667         BackgroundZoneTypeList::iterator beginGCOS = zonesGCOS.begin(), endGCOS = zonesGCOS.end();
00668 
00669         for(; beginFusion != endFusion && beginGCOS != endGCOS; beginFusion++, beginGCOS++)
00670         {
00671                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT_MESSAGE("Failed: Compare - centerx",beginFusion->centerx == beginGCOS->centerx);
00672                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT_MESSAGE("Failed: Compare - centery",beginFusion->centery == beginGCOS->centery);
00673                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT_MESSAGE("Failed: Compare - background",beginFusion->background == beginGCOS->background);
00674         }
